    <title>Adding and Subtracting Vectors</title>
    <p><em>Adding and Subtracting Vectors</em> develops the standard operations (addition, scalar multiplication) 
        for two-dimensional vectors. The graphic interpretation is shown, as well as the formal computations. 
        This lesson is the final step in the preparation for 
